      "default": "<p>Unherited was born from a simple but powerful belief: your scent should feel as original as your journey. In a fragrance market crowded with cheap imitation perfumes on one side and overpriced international luxury brands on the other, we saw a missing link — aspirational Indian consumers who value quality, honesty, and meaning. People who don't just wear a fragrance, but identify with it.</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "header",
      "content": "Colors"
    },
