          "label": "Paragraph Text",
          "default": "<p>Unherited is built for those who write their own story. Quietly, boldly, unapologetically. Every fragrance we create is crafted with intent, originality, and performance at its core. We use high-quality fragrance ingredients and high perfume oil concentrations to ensure strong sillage, long-lasting performance, and a signature scent that stays with you long after the first spray.</p>"
        }
