        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>It's about trust over tricks, consistency over discounts, and experience over excess. From uniform pricing across all platforms to thoughtful packaging and genuine customer care, every touchpoint is designed to make you feel seen, valued, and proud to be part of the journey. We are a proudly Indian fragrance brand, rooted in our culture, global in our ambition, and deeply personal in everything we do.</p>"
